entries.journal_entry_description: No one can move inventory like a Smuggler. Time to move some inventory!
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Han Solo sent you to take a job from Jake Felan in the Cantina.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Talk to Jake Felan in the Cantina
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Use the shuttle service in Hangar Bay 1.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: Use the Gamma Shuttle to Travel to Station Gamma
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Find the case of sliced weapons from within the Station Gamma.
entries.task03_comm_message_text: Not bad. Now, get to the drop off point back on Tansarii Station, bottom level. And be quiet about it. No use stirring up the locals anymore than we have to.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: You have gathered the weapons, it is now time to leave. Head to the entrance of the station, and use the shuttle service to return..
entries.task04_journal_entry_title: Use the Shuttle Service to Leave Station Gamma
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Use the elevator to go to the lower level.
entries.task05_journal_entry_title: Use the Elevator to go to the Lower Level
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Stash away the case of sliced weapons for Jake to deal with later. But be careful! Imperials lurk near the drop off point. The drop off point can be found on the bottom level of Tansarii Station in Storage Room 2.
entries.task06_journal_entry_title: Stash the case in Storage Room 2
entries.task07_comm_message_text: You're on your own. If you can resist the urge, you might want to talk the guard instead of just shooting him.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Watch out! Use your wit against the Stormtrooper and sweet-talk your way out of this one.
entries.task09_comm_message_text: Great job! You're definitely worth the price. Dump them in the receptacle. I'll get to them later. Come on back when you're done hiding the goods.
entries.task10_journal_entry_description: Whew! That was close. Dump the stash in the receptacle for Jake Felan.
entries.task11_journal_entry_description: Use the elevator to return to the main level, so you can meet with Jake.
entries.task11_journal_entry_title: Use the Elevator to return to the Main Level
entries.task12_journal_entry_description: Looks like you're in the clear. Return to Jake Felan
